        {
            "title": "A股午後跌勢加劇   滬指失3900關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後跌幅擴大，滬指失守3900關，兩市合計成交25156.14億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日跌36點或0.94%，報3897，午後跌幅擴大，低見3886點，跌47點或1.2%，為全日低位，今早低開18點或0.46%，報3915點，上午中段最高見3933，與昨日持平，全日成交11321.27億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">與9月30日黃金周前比較，升9點或0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日跌370點或2.7%，報13355點，午後見13304點，瀉421點或3.07%，跌破上午高位，今早低開92點或0.67%，報13633點，初段高報13644，跌81點或0.59%，全日成交13834.87億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">與9月30日黃金周前比較，跌171點或1.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日報4616點，跌92點或1.97%，今早低開30點或0.64%，報4679點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日報3113點，跌148點或4.55%，今早低開31點或0.95%，報3184點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股全日跌，多隻股份跌一成。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15332961-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c%e5%8b%a2%e5%8a%a0%e5%8a%87-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e5%a4%b13900%e9%97%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 15:30:21",
            "source": "bastillepost",
